---
import BaseLayout from "~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Cookie Policy">
  <article class="prose mx-auto">
    <header class="not-prose mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">Last updated: August 15, 2025</p>
    </header>

    <p>This Cookie Policy explains how we use cookies and similar technologies.</p>

    <h2>What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device to remember preferences and improve your experience.</p>

    <h2>Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Essential: Required for the site to function</li>
      <li>Analytics: Help us understand how the site is used</li>
      <li>Preferences: Remember your settings (e.g., theme)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
    <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings. Blocking some cookies may impact site functionality.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
